<h2 class="sectionedit6" id="encodage_des_videos">Encodage des vidéos</h2>
<div class="level2">

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_6'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="xbox360"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1376646693" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Encodage des vidéos] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="1468-1501" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Encodage des vidéos" /></div></form></div>
<h3 class="sectionedit7" id="xvid-mp3_avi">Xvid-MP3 (AVI)</h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>
<a href="comment_modifier_un_fichier" class="wikilink1" title="tutoriel:comment_modifier_un_fichier">encoder-avi.sh</a>
</p>
<pre class="file">#!/bin/bash
ffmpeg -y -threads 2 \
    -i mon_fichier_video.avi.mkv.mp4.mpg \
    -acodec libmp3lame -ab 128k -ac 2 \
    -vcodec libxvid -b 1M \
    -f avi mon_fichier_pour_xbox.avi</pre>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_7'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="xbox360"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1376646693" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Xvid-MP3 (AVI)] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="1502-1784" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Xvid-MP3 (AVI)" /></div></form></div>
<h3 class="sectionedit8" id="h264-aac_mp4">H264-AAC (MP4)</h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>
<a href="comment_modifier_un_fichier" class="wikilink1" title="tutoriel:comment_modifier_un_fichier">encoder-mp4.sh</a>
</p>
<pre class="file">#!/bin/bash
ffmpeg -y -threads 2 \
    -i mon_fichier_video.avi.mkv.mp4.mpg \
    -acodec libfaac -ab 128k -ac 2 \
    -vcodec libx264 -b 1M -vpre default \
    -f mp4 mon_fichier_pour_xbox.mp4
MP4Box -add mon_fichier_pour_xbox.mp4 mon_fichier_pour_xbox_lisible.mp4</pre>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_8'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="xbox360"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1376646693" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[H264-AAC (MP4)] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="1785-2150" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="H264-AAC (MP4)" /></div></form></div>
<h2 class="sectionedit9" id="transcodage">Transcodage</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
<img src="../lib/images/smileys/fixme.gif" class="icon" alt="FIXME" />
</p>

<p>
<a href="http://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/pms-linux" class="wikilink1" title="pms-linux">PS3 Media Server</a> est capable de gérer le transcodage à la volée de n&#039;importe quelle vidéo en un format lisible par la xbox.
</p>
<hr />

<p>
<em>Contributeur principal : <a href="http://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/utilisateurs/yoyomoony" class="wikilink1" title="utilisateurs:yoyomoony">yoyomoony</a>.</em>
</p>

</div>
